        Specified by:

        Specified by:

        the type of the Filter. This is one of:
        • 0 = SimpleColumnFilter

        • 2 = AheadOfScheduleFilter
        • 3 = OutsideNStandardDeviationsFilter

        • 9 = CompletedFilter
